{"tid":340090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【獨市生意】逸新收500票 擬加價加推","createTime":"2017-07-29T15:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T18:03:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e65574715f8fe591ec00c71ae6d836cb5e4faca0","tid":340090,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170729/large/1501337709_1b73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170729%2Flarge%2F1501337709_1b73.jpg&h=ecf3fc02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新盤表現平靜，市場焦點落在麗新發展（488）旗下深水埗基隆街單幢盤逸新身上，首批開價較同屬納米樓的深水埗Ava 61低逾15%，兼提供300萬元內單位，過去四天接獲約500個認購登記，較首張價單位共60伙，超額7倍。<br />\n<br />\n該公司高級副總裁潘銳民表示，逸新暫收約500票，集團對收票成績感到滿意，以本地客為主，投資者約佔四成，最快下周加推及公佈銷售安排，加推有機會加價3%至5%，最快下周內發售。"},{"pid":"16ca6837203ee0259209997bdbc8678ce77fed78","tid":340090,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff1dca7847bc4011ecdc397999040567751b9c19","tid":340090,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1%有錢人都唔止500人啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n逸新好蚊型, <br />\n<br />\ntarget都唔係有錢人"},{"pid":"f9de53f561ea26463f66e1de879a37c025ec490b","tid":340090,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:03:32.000Z","msg":"四成投資者"}]}